{"title":"Thank You, Everything: An Illustrated Love Letter to the World","link":"https://www.themarginalian.org/2024/12/12/thank-you-everything-icinori/","date":1734045342000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img width=\"320\" height=\"332\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything.jpg?fit=320%2C332&amp;ssl=1\" alt=\"Thank You, Everything: An Illustrated Love Letter to the World\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything.jpg?resize=320%2C332&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything.jpg?resize=600%2C622&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything.jpg?resize=240%2C249&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything.jpg?resize=768%2C796&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p><p>We forget that none of this had to exist — that we weren’t owed mountains and music by the universe. And maybe we have to forget — or we would be too stupefied with gratitude for every raindrop and every eyelash to get through the daily tasks punctuating the unbidden wonder of our lives. But it is good, every once in a while, to let ourselves be stupefied by gratitude, to cast upon ourselves <a href=\"https://www.themarginalian.org/2023/08/20/spell-against-indifference/\">a spell against indifference</a> by moving through the world with an inner bow at every littlest thing that prevailed over the odds of otherwise in order to exist.</p>\n<p>Artist couple Mayumi Otero and Raphael Urwiller, who work together under the pen name Icinori, offer a vibrant invitation to this countercultural way of seeing in <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Thank You, Everything</em></strong></a> (<a href=\"https://search.worldcat.org/title/1420453252?oclcNum=1420453252\" target=\"_blank\"><em>public library</em></a>) — a meditative yet exuberant journey through the world within and the world without, inspired by the Japanese notion of <em>tsuumogami</em>: the soul, or spirit, that inanimate objects are believed to acquire after being of service in the world for a hundred years. </p>\n<p>Out of what begins as an impressionistic portrait of gladness — “thank you, blue”; “thank you, morning”; “thank you, glass” — emerges a story syncopating the abstract and the concrete. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything1.jpg?resize=680%2C681&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"681\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything1.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything1.jpg?resize=320%2C321&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything1.jpg?resize=600%2C601&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything1.jpg?resize=240%2C240&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything1.jpg?resize=768%2C769&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything2.jpg?resize=680%2C679&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"679\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything2.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything2.jpg?resize=320%2C320&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything2.jpg?resize=600%2C600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything2.jpg?resize=240%2C240&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything2.jpg?resize=768%2C767&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything3.jpg?resize=680%2C681&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"681\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything3.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything3.jpg?resize=320%2C320&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything3.jpg?resize=600%2C601&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything3.jpg?resize=240%2C240&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything3.jpg?resize=768%2C769&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything4.jpg?resize=680%2C680&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"680\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything4.jpg?w=900&amp;ssl=1 900w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything4.jpg?resize=320%2C320&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything4.jpg?resize=600%2C600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything4.jpg?resize=240%2C240&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything4.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p>Day breaks with gratitude, breaks into a mysterious adventure, each step of which is a bow — we see the protagonist move through cities and landscapes, thanking every large and little thing along the way: bicycle and bus and airplane, sky and clouds and streams, night and fog, binoculars and birds, caterpillar and leaf, spring and silence. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything5.jpg?resize=680%2C340&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"340\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything5.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything5.jpg?resize=320%2C160&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything5.jpg?resize=600%2C300&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything5.jpg?resize=240%2C120&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything5.jpg?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything21-scaled.jpg?resize=680%2C459&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" heigh