sl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything24.jpg?resize=680%2C480&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything24.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything24.jpg?resize=320%2C226&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything24.jpg?resize=600%2C424&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything24.jpg?resize=240%2C169&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything24.jpg?resize=768%2C542&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything7.jpg?resize=680%2C340&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"340\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything7.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything7.jpg?resize=320%2C160&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything7.jpg?resize=600%2C300&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything7.jpg?resize=240%2C120&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything7.jpg?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything25.jpg?resize=680%2C508&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"508\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything25.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything25.jpg?resize=320%2C239&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything25.jpg?resize=600%2C448&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything25.jpg?resize=240%2C179&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything25.jpg?resize=768%2C573&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything8.jpg?resize=680%2C340&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"340\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything8.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything8.jpg?resize=320%2C160&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything8.jpg?resize=600%2C300&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything8.jpg?resize=240%2C120&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything8.jpg?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything22.jpg?resize=680%2C470&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"470\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything22.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything22.jpg?resize=320%2C221&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything22.jpg?resize=600%2C415&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything22.jpg?resize=240%2C166&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything22.jpg?resize=768%2C531&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything11.jpg?resize=680%2C680&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"680\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything11.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything11.jpg?resize=320%2C320&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything11.jpg?resize=600%2C600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything11.jpg?resize=240%2C240&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything11.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything12.jpg?resize=680%2C680&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"680\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything12.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything12.jpg?resize=320%2C320&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything12.jpg?resize=600%2C600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything12.jpg?resize=240%2C240&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything12.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p>The destination, rather than a place, is a state of being — the recompense of paying everything in our path the gratitude and reverence it is due for merely existing. For we forget, too, that dignity — this deepest reverence for being — is not something we can ever have for ourselves unless we accord it to everything and everyone else. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything10.jpg?resize=680%2C680&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"680\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything10.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything10.jpg?resize=320%2C320&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything10.jpg?resize=600%2C600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything10.jpg?resize=240%2C240&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything10.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything23.jpg?resize=680%2C427&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything23.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything23.jpg?resize=320%2C201&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything23.jpg?resize=600%2C377&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything23.jpg?resize=240%2C151&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything23.jpg?resize=768%2C482&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything9.jpg?resize=680%2C680&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"680\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything9.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything9.jpg?resize=320%2C320&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything9.jpg?resize=600%2C600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything9.jpg?resize=240%2C240&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything9.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything13.jpg?resize=680%2C680&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"680\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything13.jpg?w=900&amp;ssl=1 900w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything13.jpg?resize=320%2C320&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything13.jpg?resize=600%2C600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything13.jpg?resize=240%2C240&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoueverything13.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything20.jpg?resize=680%2C442&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"680\" height=\"442\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything20.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything20.jpg?resize=320%2C208&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything20.jpg?resize=600%2C390&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything20.jpg?resize=240%2C156&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/thankyoureverything20.jpg?resize=768%2C499&amp;ssl=1 768w\" /></a></p>\n<p>Couple <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Thank-You-Everything-Icinori/dp/1592704239/?tag=braipick-20\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Thank You, Everything</em></strong></a> with Oliver Sacks on <a href=\"https://www.themarginalian.org/2015/11/24/oliver-sacks-gratitude-book/\">gratitude and the measure of living at the horizon of death</a>, then revisit poet Marissa Davis’s <a href=\"https://www.themarginalian.org/2022/03/04/singularity-marissa-davis-toshi-reagon/\">love letter to everything alive</a>.</p>\n<p><em>Illustrations courtesy of Enchanted Lion Books; photographs by Maria Popova</em></p>\n<hr /><h3>donating = loving</h3><p>For seventeen years, I have been spending hundreds of hours and thousands of dollars each month composing <em>The Marginalian</em> (which <a href=\"https://www.themarginalian.org/2021/10/22/brain-pickings-becoming-the-marginalian/\">bore the outgrown name <em>Brain Pickings</em></a> for its first fifteen years). It has remained free and ad-free and alive thanks to patronage from readers. I have no staff, no interns, no assistant — a thoroughly one-woman labor of love that is also my life and my livelihood. If this labor makes your own life more livable in any way, please consider lending a helping hand with a <a href=\"https://www.themarginalian.org/donate/\">donation</a>. Your support makes all the difference.</p>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h3>newsletter</h3>\n<p><em>The Marginalian</em> has a free weekly newsletter. It comes out on Sundays and offers the week’s most inspiring reading. Here’s <a href=\"https://mailchi.mp/brainpickings/janna-levin-rebecca-elson-anne-lamott-james-gleick\">what to expect</a>. Like? <a href=\"https://www.themarginalian.org/newsletter/\">Sign up.</a></p>","author":"Maria Popova","siteTitle":"The Marginalian","siteHash":"052ac1be0de11784b9ef27664fbcf33da8263d0e7cb9c6e601ccd959f2d3aa78","entryHash":"cdeb65311e95e560e29316ef286be97b171574f4df57eb915a671a59aa2ba442","category":"Sites"}